{"lemma":"رِقُّ","slug":"رِقُّ","root":"ر.ق.ق","root_slug":"ر-ق-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ق-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رِقُّ","root":"رقق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16266","n16272","n16273","n16274"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%82%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be thin, fine"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be soft, tender"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pity, to sympathize, to have compassion (for)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rap (on a door)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to crush, to grind, to pulverize, to beat into a powder"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to batter, to ram"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to soften, to weaken, to relent"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become a slave"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"turtle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"parchment"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"riq, an Arabian tambourine"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bondage, slavery, servitude"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Classical Syriac ܪܩܐ (raqqā, “tortoise”) and Akkadian raqqum (“turtle, tortoise”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16266","headword_ar":"رَقَّ","root":"rq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, * Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, Mgh, K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, JK, S, Mgh, Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had the quality termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diq~apN","text_ar":"دِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA; [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aq~apu","text_ar":"الرَّقَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~iq~apu","text_ar":"الدِّقَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, the contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiyZN","text_ar":"غَلِيظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaxiynN","text_ar":"ثَخِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) [or rather, properly, it is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaxuna","text_ar":"ثَخُنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, thin"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of little thickness in comparison with its breadth and length together; little in extent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depth, between its two opposite surfaces: thin, fine, delicate, flimsy, unsubstantial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncompact, in texture &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a garment and the like:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shallow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of little depth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of water, and of sand, &c.:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wanting in spissitude;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of mud &c.:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attenuated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astrq","text_ar":"استرق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in like manner] signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstglZ","text_ar":"استغلظ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and therefore"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galuZu","text_ar":"غَلُظُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for these last two"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1130},{"kind":"text","text":"verbs are syn.]. (S, K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~ato EiZaAmuhu","text_ar":"رَقَّتْ عِظَامُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaqN","text_ar":"رَقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or both, (and if so, the second pers. may be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaqota","text_ar":"رَقَقْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiqota","text_ar":"رَقِقْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yariq~u","text_ar":"يَرِقُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaraq~u","text_ar":"يَرَقُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His bones became weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became thin, and consequently"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became aged:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) or it is said of one who has become aged. (TA. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaqN","text_ar":"رَقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below; and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a","text_ar":"رَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abject, mean, paltry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contemptible:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also 4:]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his patience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endurance, became weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakened:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak-hearted, and fearful;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a qalobuhu","text_ar":"رَقَّ قَلْبُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected with shame, shyness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bashfulness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a lahu","text_ar":"رَقَّ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, K, *) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaqotu","text_ar":"رَقَقْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender-hearted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araq~u","text_ar":"اَرَقُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"merciful, compassionate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pitiful, to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a lahu qalobuhu","text_ar":"رَقَّ لَهُ قَلْبُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trq~q","text_ar":"ترقّق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~ lahu qalobuhu","text_ar":"رَقّ لَهُ قَلْبُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b5-  [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a kalaAmuhu","text_ar":"رَقَّ كَلَامُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His speech was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, soft"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy and sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant, graceful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and see also 2. ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~ Sawotuhu","text_ar":"رَقّ صَوْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His voice was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, slender,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentle."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~ato HaAluhu","text_ar":"رَقَّتْ حَالُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, narrow in its circumstances,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below, and 4; and see also 4 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xf","text_ar":"خف"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a Eayo$uhu","text_ar":"رَقَّ عَيْشُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His living,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sustenance, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, scanty."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a Eadaduhu","text_ar":"رَقَّ عَدَدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His years that he numbered were for the most part passed, so that the remainder was little"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyq","text_ar":"رَقِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his estimation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~a","text_ar":"رَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~N","text_ar":"رِقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, a slave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Mgh, Msb, K; *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he remained a slave."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~ahu","text_ar":"رَقَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arq~hu","text_ar":"ارقّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him a slave:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or ↓ the latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he kept him as a slave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEotaqapu","text_ar":"اَعْتَقَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astrq~hu","text_ar":"استرقّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or ↓ the second and ↓ third,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he possessed him as a slave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~ahu","text_ar":"رَقَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; accord. to ISk and Az and others: (TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astrq~hu","text_ar":"استرقّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took him as, a slave;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he brought him into a state of slavery."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","TA","JK","Mgh","K"]},{"entry_id":"n16272","headword_ar":"رَقٌّ","root":"rq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruq~N","text_ar":"رُقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also, (JK, S, Mgh, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~N","text_ar":"رِقٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) but the latter is a rare dial. var. though some read thus in the Kur lii. 3, (Msb,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Parchment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vellum;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the present day; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which one writes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K:) or (so accord. to the Mgh, but in the K “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a white"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blank"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfap","text_ar":"صَحِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paper"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but generally such as is written upon]: (JK, Mgh, K:) or metaphorically applied to (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a skin written upon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly one upon which one writes: (Bd in lii. 3:) accord. to Fr, (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHaAy^if","text_ar":"صَحَايِف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"papers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"records,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that will be produced to the sons of Adam on the day of resurrection;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which indicates that such as is written is also thus termed: (Az, TA:) in the Kur lii. 3, [accord. to some,] applied to (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Book of the Law revealed to Moses:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Kur-án."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel.)       -A3-  Also, (K,) or the former word [only], (JK, S, Msb,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tortoise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great tortoise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male tortoise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crocodile:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) or, (K,) accord. to Ibráheem El-Harbee, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain aquatic reptile,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) [app. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"turtle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sea-tortoise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having four legs, and claws,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nails, and teeth in a head which it exposes and conceals, and which is killed for food:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruquwqN","text_ar":"رُقُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A'Obeyd, JK, S, Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","Mgh","Msb","K","Az","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n16273","headword_ar":"رُقٌّ","root":"rq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shallow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to water; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shallow water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N raqiyqN","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ رَقِيقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; IDrd, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not copious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not abundant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, TA;) in a sea, or great river, or in a valley; (IDrd, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~N","text_ar":"رَقٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1131},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqaAriqN","text_ar":"رُقَارِقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IDrd, K.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaAqN","text_ar":"رَقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n16274","headword_ar":"رِقٌّ","root":"rq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raq~N","text_ar":"رَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [It is indicated in the K that it is syn. with the latter word in all of its (the latter's) senses: but I do not find it to be so in any other lexicon.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thin thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. [There expl. as signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'N raqiyqN","text_ar":"شَىْءٌ رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but perhaps by this may be meant that it is an epithet"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as it is said to be in the K.]) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaves of trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branches that are easy for the cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to eat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain thorny plant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqaAqN","text_ar":"رَقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, of a slave; slavery; servitude;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, Msb, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~iy~apN","text_ar":"رِقِّيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (KL.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}